OL,3,CWales' first Oscar winner: Blue plaque
OL,4,Cunveiled for Hollywood legend Ray
OL,5,CMilland
OL,7,FA blue plaque to remember Ray Milland,
OL,8,Fthe first Welsh actor to win an Oscar,
OL,9,Fhas been unveiled in his hometown of
OL,10,FNeath.
OL,12,FMilland's starring performance as an
OL,13,Falcoholic writer in Billy Wilder's
OL,14,F'The Lost Weekend' earned him Best
OL,15,FActor at the Academy Awards, along
OL,16,Fwith the same accolade at Cannes and a
OL,17,FGolden Globe.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
