OL,3,CWales' first Oscar winner: Blue plaque
OL,4,Cunveiled for Hollywood legend Ray
OL,5,CMilland
OL,7,FUnder contract with Paramount for
OL,8,Fnearly 20 years, he was one of the
OL,9,Fhighest paid actors in Hollywood in
OL,10,Fthe late 1940s.
OL,12,FLater, he forged an enduring career as
OL,13,Fa television actor and director,
OL,14,Fworking up until the year before his
OL,15,Fdeath in 1986.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
