OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772917926
OL,3,CWales' first Oscar winner: Blue plaque
OL,4,Cunveiled for Hollywood legend Ray
OL,5,CMilland
OL,7,F"1928 to 1985 - I don't think there
OL,8,Fare many careers in Hollywood that
OL,9,Flasted as long" says Jonathan Davies,
OL,10,FChair of Neath Antiquarian Society,
OL,11,Fwho made the formal request for the
OL,12,Fplaque.
OL,14,F"He was in film noir, he was in
OL,15,Fcomedies, he was in horror films, he
OL,16,Facted in the theatre! This man had an
OL,17,Fincredible career, and we have
OL,18,Fdeservedly given him the blue plaque
OL,19,Fand the recognition he deserves in
OL,20,FNeath".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
